descriptionNullable:
This dataset is used for food classification. One can use this dataset to build a classifier model. Different categories of food items present are : 
1. Bread
2. Dairy Product
3. Dessert
4. Egg
5. Fried Food
6. Meat
7. Noodles-Pasta
8. Rice
9. Seafood
10. Soup
11. Vegetable-Fruit
Using these categories, one can train the model and can predict for images present in the test category.
